title: Digital Grampa 2000 - Penny Pony Rides
description:
Hey kids, DG2K here with my debut album 'Penny Pony Rides.'

Here's what Denvertronic.com had to say about my album: "...a fabulous release from Digital Grampa 2000 that spans a wide gamut of genres. It is rough, and some of the tracks could be described as experimental, noise, industrial, gabber, as well as a few crunkified slowed-down beats to give the thing even more flavor."

It ain't background music, that's for sure, but I hope you guys enjoy it enough to send copies to your friends and seed it.

Thanks for your support!

Change.

DG2K
